      "role": "user",
      "content": "but u said it's \"misguided\" to see it as a tool for censorship. isnt that just dismissing what a lot of people are actually experiencing? like, if people are being deplatformed or can't speak their minds because they're afraid of being called names, isnt that censorship regardless of what the \"underlying principles\" are?",
